Package it.polimi.ingsw.Model

Interface GodPower

All Known Implementing Classes:
Apollo, Artemis, Athena, Atlas, DefaultDivinity, Demeter, Hephaestus, Minotaur, Pan, Prometheus
public interface GodPower
This class represents the god power that a player can choose at the start of the game. It contains a method (execute(Player, Cell, int)) that is used instead of the normal move/build
See Also:
Game, Player, Worker

    • execute

      void execute​(Player player, Cell destination, int worker) throws AthenaException
      This method is used from the player when he wants to use the power of the God instead of making a move or a build
      Parameters:
      player - who's making the action
      destination - where to move or build with the god power
      worker - who's moving or building
      Throws:
      AthenaException - if it's moving up but Athena's power is active
